overview: One of IMPACT Wrestling's biggest nights of the year will feature Deonna Purrazzo defending her Knockouts Championship against Kylie Rae, The Motor City Machine Guns taking on The North, The Good Brothers, and Ace Austin & Madman Fulton in a four-way match for the IMPACT Tag Team Championships, and Eric Young defends his IMPACT World Heavyweight Championship against Rich Swann.
title: IMPACT Wrestling: Bound for Glory
